data.description: I want a nice house with a little bit of space, right?? This is what all the buyers ask us for! Look no further! This is a great listing! Home features 1.5 stories, 4 BR and 2 BA situated on almost 1/2 an acre; study niche area plus dining room; tile floors throughout main area; family room with cozy wood burning fireplace; spacious kitchen with tons of cabinets and counter top space; new dish washer and refrigerator is included; master bedroom in rear of home with double sinks, soaking tub and separate shower; 1 bedroom plus a bonus area upstairs is perfect for the teenager in your family; fresh paint and carpets just cleaned; huge fenced back yard and NO RESTRICTIONS here! Conveniently located to Valley Ranch Town Center, Highway 59 and the Grand Parkway
